{
  "uuid": "dcdbc777d3f0cd6cbc1b71a7bee85bc8",
  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Logistics Coordinator",
  "description": "<p><strong>#Sales Admin #Logistics #Data #Operations #Warehouse #Car Accessories</strong></p><p><strong>Salary Package:</strong> SGD1800 - SGD3500 commensurate with experience</p><p><strong>Job Location:</strong> Singapore West Lok Yang, near Pioneer MRT Station</p><p><strong>Job Types:</strong> Permanent, Full time, Onsite, 5 days</p><p><strong>Business Sector:</strong> Automotive Accessories Distribution, Wholesale, Customization & Solutions Provider</p><p>Prior experience in Automotive Industry logistics or operations is preferred; however, motivated fresh graduates with a strong willingness to learn are welcome to apply!</p><p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p><p><strong>Data Processing & Coordination</strong>:</p><ul><li><p>Liaise with operations and warehouse teams to ensure accurate data processing.</p></li><li><p>Receive stock checklists and load items to the store using a trolley.</p></li><li><p>Prioritize and allocate pick-and-pass picking orders to courier service companies for efficient export and local deliveries.</p></li><li><p>Update information into the system in a timely manner.</p></li><li><p>Perform any other warehouse administrative duties as assigned.</p></li></ul><p><strong>Store Management</strong>:</p><ul><li><p>Oversee the management of store operations and inventory.</p></li></ul><p><strong>Inventory Management</strong>:</p><ul><li><p>Oversee inventory levels of car accessories, ensuring adequate stock to meet customer demand.</p></li><li><p>Track product movement and forecast inventory needs based on sales trends.</p></li><li><p>Maintain accurate records of stock, monitor stock rotation, and manage stock replenishment.</p></li></ul><p><strong>Order Processing & Fulfillment</strong>:</p><ul><li><p>Ensure accurate and timely processing of customer orders, both online and in-store.</p></li><li><p>Coordinate the preparation, packaging, and shipping of products.</p></li><li><p>Work with suppliers to ensure timely delivery of car accessories.</p></li></ul><p><strong>Logistics Coordination</strong>:</p><ul><li><p>Coordinate with shipping companies and logistics providers for the delivery of products.</p></li><li><p>Track the status of deliveries and resolve any issues related to shipment delays or errors.</p></li></ul><p><strong>Sales Support</strong>:</p><ul><li><p>Collaborate closely with the sales team to understand customer needs and ensure product availability.</p></li></ul><p><strong>Customer Service</strong>:</p><ul><li><p>Address customer queries related to order status, shipping, and product availability.</p></li><li><p>Monitor returns and exchanges, ensuring proper handling in line with store policies.</p></li></ul><p><strong>Data Analysis & Reporting</strong>:</p><ul><li><p>Monitor and report on inventory levels and fulfillment rates.</p></li></ul><p>Job Types: Full-time, Permanent, Fresh graduate</p><p>Work Location: In person</p><p>Benefits:</p><ul><li><p>Additional leave</p></li><li><p>Free parking</p></li><li><p>Professional development</p></li></ul><p><a href=\"https://sg.jobstreet.com/Logistics-Coordinator-jobs/full-time\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"></a></p>",
